==LOL WUT==
The PATRIOT ACT, named using traditional Orwellian Doublethink, made provisions allowing [[police|teh fuzz]] to perform warrantless searches and seizures and to arrest and imprison suspects (read: [[muslim|filthy, turban-wearing jihadis]]) indefinitely without bail, as well as warrantless wiretapping.  Nobody gave a shit for [[at least 100]] days, since the [[CIA]] had been pulling the same crap since [[at least 100 years ago]] and minorities were already used to being [[raep]]ed by [[The Man|the police]].

